^xE05030Make sure to fill out your resistances, you want 75% fire/cold/lightning resist. it doesn&apos;t matter which pieces have the resist.^7

^x70FF70Weapon^7: You want the highest dps ele/phys weapon you can afford, preferable on a gemini base (additional arrow).
^x70FF70Quiver^7: Just good dps stats, high flat/bow dmg or projectile speed with attack speed. 
^x70FF70amulet^7: Preferable want +proj levels, besides that aim for life/resist. If you get 30 spirit you can swap Summon Companion for Rhoa mount
^x70FF70Chest^7: you want the highest evasion chest you can afford. 
^xFFFF77Rarity^7 is still really good in 0.3, You would try to hit at least 100% if you want to farm efficiently (don&apos;t focus on this if you feel like you&apos;re lacking damage or defense)
^xAF6025Jewels on tree^7: Just looking for generic damage: attack damage, elemental damage, movement speed, bonus from quivers, projectile damage, attack speed, etc

^xE05030!!!!important!!!!^7
You&apos;ll want 1 sapphire jewel with mana on kill to sustain mana during mapping.

